This paper describe tools used for researching and building the project.


# frontend / web 

http://www.initializr.com/
html5 boilerplate template generator, very usefull for starting a website from scratch with all needed configuration
normalizer, bootstrap, google analytics, jquery local and remote loading, etc...

# dealing with forms and models
http://wtforms.readthedocs.org/en/latest/crash_course.html#editing-existing-objects

# data fields
http://wtforms.readthedocs.org/en/latest/fields.html#basic-fields

